                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290219-131-off747 t18290219-131-crimeloc750"></join>. I did not miss these articles till the officer brought them on the 15th of January; I had seen them safe about a week before; I know nothing of the prisoner.</p>

               <p>Cross-examined by MR. BODKIN. Q. How long before had you seen them? A. About a week; I have a lad who occasionally serves: I had no more of this colour in my shop.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>One witness gave the prisoner a good character.</p>
